def save_profile_picture(file: UploadFile):
    ext = os.path.splitext(file.filename)[1]
    filename = f"{uuid.uuid4()}{ext}"
    filepath = f"media/photos/{filename}"
    with open(filepath, "wb") as buffer:
        buffer.write(file.file.read())
    return filepath
